item.title: How to use New Renaissance Thinking to build an extraordinary business
item.description:
In this episode we talk with Perry Marshall - best selling author of 8 books including The Ultimate Guide to Google Ads, The Ultimate Guide to Facebook Ads, the Definitive Guide to TikTok ads, and 80/20 sales and marketing - about his revolutionary new approach to business thinking called New Renaissance.
